casebody.data:
Eric Jamal WHITLEY
v.
Donnie HARRISON No. 386P17 Supreme Court of North Carolina. November 17, 2017 Eric Jamal Whitley, for Whitley, Eric Jamal. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, for Harrison, Donnie (Sheriff of Wake).

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 16th of November 2017 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Wake County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 17th of November 2017."
